            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "The question is, what you want to archive here?\nIf you want to link a group to another group to use identical settings:\n`hi link GroupA GroupB`   -- As I understand you want this?\n\nIf you want to set additional settings like italic, bold, underline etc...\n`hi Group guifg=#ff0000 guibg=#00ff00 gui=bold,italic`\n\nHighlighting follows precedence and can add or override each other. Either in regex highlighting and treesitter highlighting. So it depends which highlighting we are talking about... (regex, treesitter or semantic token highlighting)",
