        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I don't think you understand my proposition. Simply be able to display multiple highlights at once.\n\nHowever, given your comments, I am now a bit more unsure.\n\nShould `:hi <A> <B> guifg=#123123` be valid? I think if `:hi <A> <B>` displayed 2 groups, then people would assume so.\n\nNow, the proposal seems like an unecessary complication - but I'll keep it open for others to comment.",
